    • 构造器详细资料

      • UserGUI_Return

        public UserGUI_Return​(int available,
                      int total,
                      java.lang.String IDNum,
                      int buttonChecker)
        The return page, the user can click the slot which is distributed by the system to return.
        参数:
        available - the number of scooters available in the station.
        total - the number of scooters a station can carry.
        IDNum - The user's QM number
        buttonChecker - the station which is chose by user to return a scooter.
